Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.49,0:23:44.16,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,探险！发现！游乐设施！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.16,0:23:46.49,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,今天要介绍的是「奶油古董店」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:48.45,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,等一下 这是最后一回了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:50.25,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,还有这个「NO IMAGE」是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:51.46,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:54.33,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,「奶油古董店」充满梦想的商店
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.33,0:23:56.13,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,大家都喜欢的「奶油古董店」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:57.54,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,不用重复那么多遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.54,0:23:59.59,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,大家都来的「奶油古董店」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.59,0:24:02.42,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,哦 是什么宣传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:05.01,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,嗯 请多关照「奶油古董店」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:07.43,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,虽然我也不知道是什么商店
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:09.52,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,你去了解一下啊！
