Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:50.72,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}恋に焦がれてゆくの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:53.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}天にも登る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:56.72,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}ねぇ　夢心地いい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:01.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}浮ついている台風は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:05.61,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}誰にも止められない
